POST {{baseUrl}}/api/oauth/organizations/{{orgUuid}}/admin_requests
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
x-organization-uuid: {{orgUuid}}
Content-Type: application/json
User-Agent: claude-code/{{cliVersion}}

{
    "request_type": "limit_increase",
    "details": null
}

### Response:
# (CLI ignores response body; server returns JSON)

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 4.5 List My Admin Requests
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
