# @name listMyAdminRequests
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/oauth/organizations/{{orgUuid}}/admin_requests/me?request_type=limit_increase&statuses=pending&statuses=dismissed
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
x-organization-uuid: {{orgUuid}}
User-Agent: claude-code/{{cliVersion}}

### Response:
# [ ... ]

