### 8.3 List Batches
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# @name listBatches
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/messages/batches?beta=true
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}
anthropic-version: {{version}}
# message-batches-2024-09-24 graduated to GA in v2.1.63

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 8.4 Cancel Batch
