POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/messages/batches/{{batchId}}/cancel?beta=true
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}
anthropic-version: {{version}}
# message-batches-2024-09-24 graduated to GA in v2.1.63

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 8.5 Delete Batch
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

