### ============================================================================
### SECTION 24: SESSION PERSISTENCE (with Session Token)
### ============================================================================
# Pattern: rg "session_ingress|Last-Uuid" cli.js

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 24.1 Persist Session Log Entry (PUT)
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Used for session log synchronization with Last-Uuid header for conflict detection

# @name persistSessionLog
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v1/session_ingress/session/{{sessionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Last-Uuid: {{lastUuid}}

{
    "uuid": "{{entryUuid}}",
    "data": {}
}

### Response:
# 200/201 - Success
# 409 - Conflict (UUID mismatch)
# 401 - Token expired

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 24.2 Fetch Session Logs
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Same URL as PUT, different method - GET fetches, PUT persists

# @name fetchSessionLogs
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/session_ingress/session/{{sessionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

### Response:
# {
#   "loglines": [...]
# }


